<bibRefCitation id="B82A7AFE9A024344FD9BC8FCFD7435B7" author="ASSING V" box="[638,690,1513,1535]" pageId="6" pageNumber="1241" pagination="51 - 67" refId="ref7213" refString="ASSING V. (2005): A revision of Othiini. XIV. New species, new synonyms, and new records (Insecta: Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). - Entomological Problems 35 (1): 51 - 67." type="journal article" year="2005">2005</bibRefCitation>
